These are Puzzles for 3x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, musical, family
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, thai, turkish
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, snowmobile, ship
1. the person driving the ship is in an even position##4
2. the thai is on the left of the indian##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the thai is in an even position##4
5. the person watching family movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | family       | drama     | musical    |
| Nationality   | turkish   | thai          | indian   |
| Transport         | taxi | ship | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, cabbage, nectarine
3 different pets are kept: snake, turtle, hedgehog
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, boat, motorbike
1. the person driving the motorbike is the person eating nectarine##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
3. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the person driving the motorbike is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Food    | avocado     | nectarine  | cabbage  |
| Pet   | hedgehog | turtle | snake    |
| Transport     | roller      | motorbike    | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-3::.
House: art-deco, victorian, modern
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop, reggae
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, mauve, light-blue
1. the person who likes chestnut is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes light-blue is the art-deco house##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of funk##1
4. the modern house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
5. the modern house is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |
| House          | art-deco         | modern     | victorian   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop       | funk     | reggae |
| Color         | light-blue | chestnut | mauve |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, drawing, magic-tricks
The people have 3 different jobs:  social-worker, teacher, writer
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, british, american
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the american##1
2. the british is on the right of the writer##1
3. the social-worker is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left##1
5. the writer is on the far left or far right##3
6. the teacher is on the right of the writer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2     |       3       |
| Hobby   | skydiving | magic-tricks  | drawing |
| Job        | writer | teacher  | social-worker |
| Nationality        | malaysian | british | american         |

