.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-5::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, poppy, azalea
There are 3 different nationalities: american, australian, chinese
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, vegafina, chaman
1. the american is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
2. the australian is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
4. the oliveros-smoker is in an odd position##4
5. the person who growsazalea is on the far left##1
6. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |
| Flower   | azalea | daffodil  | poppy  |
| Nationality   | australian  | american | chinese |
| Cigar           | vegafina  | chaman    | oliveros    |

