.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-6::.
3 different pets are kept: hamster, dog, fish
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, musical, mystery
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, car, quad-bike
1. the owner of the hamster is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person watching mystery movies##2
2. the person watching thriller movies is the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
4. the person driving the car is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |      3      |
| Pet    | fish  | hamster  | dog        |
| Movie-Genre       | mystery | musical | thriller |
| Transport   | boat    | car   | quad-bike   |

