.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-7::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, chess, gardening
House: palace, cottage, cape-cod
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, skateboarding, tennis
1. the person who's hobby is chess is between the palace house and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
2. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |    3    |
| Hobby   | puzzles | chess        | gardening |
| House           | palace   | cottage      | cape-cod     |
| Sport         | tennis | skateboarding | golf    |

