.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-8::.
City: rome, london, liverpool
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, photographer, pilot
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, brazilian, american
1. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
2. the argentine is between the pilot and the person traveling to liverpool##2
3. the photographer is on the right of the argentine##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is in an odd position##4
5. the american is the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |      3       |
| City    | rome   | london | liverpool       |
| Job     | pilot  | musician  | photographer |
| Nationality   | brazilian | argentine  | american       |

