.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, collecting, rock-climbing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, zombie, drama
3 different games are played: chess, whist, bridge
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person watching action movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
4. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person playing chess and the person who's hobby is collecting##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | collecting | camping | rock-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | drama       | zombie  | action     |
| Game           | whist     | bridge     | chess          |

