.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-10::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, quad-bike, train
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, time-travel
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, baccarat, prince
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the prince-smoker##3
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3    |
| Transport           | train | snowmobile        | quad-bike   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | time-travel | epic    |
| Cigar   | prince         | oliveros      | baccarat |

