There are 3 different nationalities: thai, egyptian, mexican
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, scooter, skateboard
1. the person who's birthday is in february is the thai##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4
3. the mexican is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2      |    3    |
| Birthday         | february | october      | march  |
| Nationality         | thai         | mexican      | egyptian    |
| Transport   | bike         | skateboard | scooter |

