The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, begonia, bellflower
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, disco, funk
1. the person who growsbegonia is the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who growsdahlia is in an even position##4
3. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of funk##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |      3       |
| Hobby         | singing        | dancing  | writing      |
| Flower           | bellflower | dahlia | begonia |
| Music-Genre   | disco        | rock   | funk  |

