.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-13::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, mystery, crime
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, golf, water-polo
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, reggae, dubstep
1. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
3. the person watching mystery movies is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Movie-Genre    | animation        | mystery | crime     |
| Sport       | basketball | golf          | water-polo |
| Music-Genre   | reggae     | dubstep          | r&b       |

