.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-15::.
3 different games are played: domino, mah-jongg, scrabble
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, r&b, trance
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, june, october
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the fan of punk is the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is the fan of r&b##1
5. the person playing scrabble is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |   3    |
| Game   | mah-jongg      | scrabble | domino |
| Music-Genre   | r&b        | punk         | trance |
| Birthday           | may | october         | june   |

