.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-16::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, water-polo, surfing
House: craftsman, palace, ranch-style
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, romance, superhero
1. the person watching superhero movies is the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
5. the craftsman house is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
6. the person who's sport is surfing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Sport         | water-polo   | basketball     | surfing   |
| House           | palace  | craftsman | ranch-style |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | romance     | disaster |

