.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-17::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, pilot, social-worker
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, bluemaster, havana
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, azalea, tulip
1. the person who growstulip is on the far left##1
2. the paramedic is in an even position##4
3. the social-worker is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
4. the pilot is the bluemaster-smoker##1
5. the havana-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Job     | pilot      | paramedic | social-worker |
| Cigar     | bluemaster | tiparillo      | havana           |
| Flower   | tulip | amaryllis  | azalea    |

