The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, may, april
3 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, go
1. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person playing go##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | fanta  | almond-milk |
| Birthday   | november  | april    | may       |
| Game   | snooker   | go | scrabble   |

