.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-20::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, september, march
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, documentary, musical
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, siglo, fonseca
1. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person watching documentary movies##2
2. the fonseca-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the fonseca-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching musical movies is the siglo-smoker##1
5. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
7. the person watching crime movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Birthday         | march      | september | december |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | crime      | musical    |
| Cigar           | fonseca      | bluemaster        | siglo       |

 